688
00:26:03,220 --> 00:26:04,460
Then, I'll bite you.

689
00:26:06,020 --> 00:26:06,940
Stop!

690
00:26:08,860 --> 00:26:10,540
You bad woman, how dare you bite me!

691
00:26:10,820 --> 00:26:11,900
