697
00:26:32,700 --> 00:26:34,100
The steamed bun isn't necessary.

698
00:26:34,100 --> 00:26:35,140
You want food, don't you?

699
00:26:35,140 --> 00:26:36,300
Will you let me eat?

700
00:26:36,300 --> 00:26:37,860
I'll make you see it but not eat it.

701
00:26:37,860 --> 00:26:38,700
Psychopath.

702
00:26:38,710 --> 00:26:39,580
What did you say?

703
00:26:40,500 --> 00:26:41,460
I said, any pancake?

704
00:26:56,060 --> 00:26:56,980
When I'm out,

705
00:26:57,260 --> 00:26:59,020
you'd better not fall into my hands.

706
00:26:59,700 --> 00:27:00,620
What are you muttering?

707
00:27:01,220 --> 00:27:02,940
Nothing. I'm working.

708
00:27:09,370 --> 00:27:10,220
