716
00:27:27,420 --> 00:27:28,700
After staying here for long,

717
00:27:28,860 --> 00:27:30,300
I have an inside track.

718
00:27:31,620 --> 00:27:32,540
Are you all right?

719
00:27:32,900 --> 00:27:34,180
I'm fine. Still alive.

720
00:27:34,500 --> 00:27:36,180
I've been watching you for a while.

721
00:27:36,500 --> 00:27:37,900
You're really foolhardy.

722
00:27:41,420 --> 00:27:43,020
Miserable fate.

723
00:27:43,420 --> 00:27:44,660
Tragic destiny.

724
00:27:46,220 --> 00:27:47,780
One single mistake led to total failure.

725
00:27:49,040 --> 00:27:51,180
Do you know why this place exists?

726
00:27:53,550 --> 00:27:54,420
Is it because

727
00:27:54,420 --> 00:27:55,580
the evil Magistrate Meng

728
00:27:55,580 --> 00:27:57,820
wants everybody to get married?

729
00:27:57,980 --> 00:27:58,900
No.

730
00:28:00,300 --> 00:28:01,380
Because it's a place

731
00:28:02,900 --> 00:28:04,900
for disciplining women.

732
00:28:05,740 --> 00:28:06,660
Discipline?

733
00:28:07,580 --> 00:28:08,500
How?

734
00:28:10,700 --> 00:28:12,300
- By torturing them.
- Torturing?

735
00:28:12,590 --> 00:28:13,460
It's another word

736
00:28:13,460 --> 00:28:14,460
for "punishing".

737
00:28:17,900 --> 00:28:19,060
Do you want to get out?

738
00:28:20,660 --> 00:28:21,580
You can do that?

739
00:28:25,100 --> 00:28:26,420
I can't tell you.

740
00:28:26,780 --> 00:28:27,620
Why?

741
00:28:27,620 --> 00:28:28,900
Because what we have to do

742
00:28:28,900 --> 00:28:29,820
is rather risky.

743
00:28:30,180 --> 00:28:31,180
If you're caught,

744
00:28:31,180 --> 00:28:32,380
you'll be terribly tortured.

745
00:28:32,540 --> 00:28:34,300
Now, I'm already terribly tortured.

746
00:28:34,300 --> 00:28:35,220
No.

747
00:28:36,060 --> 00:28:37,100
If you're caught,

748
00:28:38,740 --> 00:28:39,740
you'll blame me.

749
00:28:43,340 --> 00:28:44,540
Why would I blame you?

750
00:28:45,420 --> 00:28:46,260
When you appeared

751
00:28:46,260 --> 00:28:47,460
with the food,

752
00:28:48,780 --> 00:28:49,700
I knew

753
00:28:49,860 --> 00:28:51,340
you were a heaven-sent angel.

754
00:28:56,780 --> 00:28:58,180
It feels so good

755
00:28:59,300 --> 00:29:00,220
to be trusted.

756
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:02,340
No time to waste.

757
00:29:02,340 --> 00:29:03,300
I'm taking you out now.

758
00:29:03,680 --> 00:29:04,880
- All right.
- Let's go.

759
00:29:12,740 --> 00:29:13,580
Kan,

760
00:29:13,580 --> 00:29:14,460
you looked calm.

761
00:29:14,460 --> 00:29:15,340
Any solution?

762
00:29:15,340 --> 00:29:16,260
No.

763
00:29:16,460 --> 00:29:18,100
No? Then why...?

764
00:29:18,780 --> 00:29:20,580
Guiwei, remember.

765
00:29:20,980 --> 00:29:22,980
A man lives on his dignity.

766
00:29:23,540 --> 00:29:24,980
The worse the situation is,

767
00:29:24,980 --> 00:29:26,420
the more confidence you must fake.

768
00:29:26,620 --> 00:29:27,820
Sometimes, as you keep faking,

769
00:29:28,060 --> 00:29:29,100
it will really work out.

770
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:32,420
Why aren't you excited to hear

771
00:29:32,420 --> 00:29:33,460
such inspiring words?

772
00:29:33,460 --> 00:29:34,780
When Sixi said this to you,

773
00:29:34,780 --> 00:29:35,700
I was also there.

774
00:29:38,740 --> 00:29:40,380
There's a steamed bun shop nearby.

775
00:29:40,700 --> 00:29:41,660
Steamed bun?

776
00:29:41,660 --> 00:29:42,580
There isn't any.

777
00:29:43,100 --> 00:29:44,100
Not at all.

778
00:29:44,240 --> 00:29:45,100
Are you sure?

779
00:29:45,100 --> 00:29:46,300
Why have you been selling

780
00:29:46,300 --> 00:29:47,340
tea leaves instead of fish?

781
00:29:47,340 --> 00:29:48,980
I met a very kind man.

782
00:29:49,260 --> 00:29:51,540
He thought I earned
very little money from fish.

783
00:29:51,780 --> 00:29:53,020
So, he gave me some tea leaves.

784
00:29:53,220 --> 00:29:54,260
I'll sell them, then.

785
00:29:54,580 --> 00:29:55,580
Who's that man?

786
00:29:55,580 --> 00:29:57,500
Such a great man in our county.

787
00:29:57,860 --> 00:29:59,420
He isn't a local guy.

788
00:29:59,740 --> 00:30:01,100
He's Tea Master.

789
00:30:01,380 --> 00:30:02,620
Who exactly is he?

790
00:30:03,460 --> 00:30:05,460
You don't even know him?

791
00:30:05,900 --> 00:30:08,580
He's a man who makes great tea.

792
00:30:10,260 --> 00:30:11,300
Kan, how about

793
00:30:11,300 --> 00:30:12,460
we check somewhere else?

794
00:30:14,060 --> 00:30:14,980
Watch and learn.

795
00:30:18,660 --> 00:30:20,540
I've heard you sell tea leaves.

796
00:30:21,260 --> 00:30:22,180
How do you know?

797
00:30:24,180 --> 00:30:26,140
I knew it from my best friend,

798
00:30:26,140 --> 00:30:27,580
Tea Master.

799
00:30:28,620 --> 00:30:30,700
You're his friend?

800
00:30:32,140 --> 00:30:33,900
The closest friend.

801
00:30:35,900 --> 00:30:37,540
Two taels of silver for half a jin.

802
00:30:38,020 --> 00:30:38,940
Two taels?

803
00:30:39,140 --> 00:30:40,220
Way too expensive.

804
00:30:40,220 --> 00:30:41,140
Don't interrupt.

805
00:30:43,980 --> 00:30:45,020
How about this?

806
00:30:45,020 --> 00:30:46,140
I give you four taels

807
00:30:47,020 --> 00:30:47,980
and you'll tell me

808
00:30:48,260 --> 00:30:49,420
where the Tea Master is.

809
00:30:49,620 --> 00:30:51,020
But you're his friend.

810
00:30:51,020 --> 00:30:52,500
Why do you not know that?

811
00:30:52,500 --> 00:30:54,260
Well, umm...

812
00:30:54,460 --> 00:30:56,100
We lost contact for a long time.

813
00:30:56,340 --> 00:30:57,500
But you just said

814
00:30:57,500 --> 00:30:58,700
he told you

815
00:30:58,700 --> 00:30:59,820
about the tea leaves here.

816
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:03,100
Kids just don't know

817
00:31:03,100 --> 00:31:03,940
the adult thing.

818
00:31:03,940 --> 00:31:05,100
He moved away, huh?

819
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:06,620
That's right.

820
00:31:06,900 --> 00:31:07,780
He has moved away.

821
00:31:07,780 --> 00:31:08,820
That's the thing.

822
00:31:08,820 --> 00:31:09,780
How about this?

823
00:31:09,780 --> 00:31:10,740
You give me ten taels.

824
00:31:11,180 --> 00:31:12,660
I won't give you tea leaves,

825
00:31:12,660 --> 00:31:14,140
but tell you where he lives.

826
00:31:14,140 --> 00:31:14,980
Ten?

827
00:31:14,980 --> 00:31:16,220
That's not too much, is it?

828
00:31:17,460 --> 00:31:18,460
Listen, Kan.

829
00:31:18,460 --> 00:31:19,580
This boy is tricky.

830
00:31:19,580 --> 00:31:20,500
Don't let him fool you.

831
00:31:26,820 --> 00:31:27,740
Take this.

832
00:31:28,420 --> 00:31:29,340
Go away.

833
00:31:33,060 --> 00:31:33,980
Hey, boy.

834
00:31:34,540 --> 00:31:36,060
You'll be very promising.

835
00:31:37,460 --> 00:31:38,380
You just gave him that?

836
00:31:38,660 --> 00:31:39,580
Watch and learn.

837
00:31:39,580 --> 00:31:40,900
I can't learn anything.

838
00:31:44,260 --> 00:31:46,860
I won't talk back
when my husband curses me.

839
