847
00:32:10,180 --> 00:32:11,100
Here?

848
00:32:11,420 --> 00:32:12,980
Outside the wall is Sipo Bay.

849
00:32:13,140 --> 00:32:14,500
A lot of ghosts haunt there.

850
00:32:14,730 --> 00:32:15,620
Will you be scared?

851
00:32:15,620 --> 00:32:16,540
Scared?

852
00:32:16,860 --> 00:32:18,420
Even ghosts will be tortured here.

853
00:32:18,580 --> 00:32:19,660
Everybody has to work here.

854
00:32:19,780 --> 00:32:21,180
Nobody can live an easy life here.

855
00:32:21,180 --> 00:32:22,050
What else scares me?

856
00:32:22,050 --> 00:32:22,900
At this critical time,

857
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:24,500
the rhyme isn't necessary.

858
00:32:25,460 --> 00:32:26,580
Keep this in mind.

859
00:32:26,860 --> 00:32:27,740
Pass the Sipo Bay

860
00:32:27,740 --> 00:32:29,220
and you'll go straight to Sheji Altar.

861
00:32:29,220 --> 00:32:30,580
Then you'll reach Jianping Academy.

862
00:32:30,820 --> 00:32:31,660
If we get separated,

863
00:32:31,660 --> 00:32:33,980
we'll meet there, all right?

864
00:32:33,980 --> 00:32:34,900
Got it.

865
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:36,100
Tie up your dress.

866
00:32:36,260 --> 00:32:37,180
Alright.

867
00:32:41,420 --> 00:32:42,340
You go first.

868
00:32:42,620 --> 00:32:43,820
No. I'll go after you.

